
--- USER MANUAL ---
Before running any flask app, activate de moduleÂ´s virtual env:
$ . venv/bin/activate

To deactivate the virtualenv:
$ deactivate

To run a flask app, and enable all development features:
$ export FLASK_APP=<app name>
$ export FLASK_ENV=development
$ flask run

'flaskr' app custom cli commands:
$ flask init-db # to initialize the sqlite db for a flaskr app instance

Whenever creating a new app instance, a new database must be created for it.
So the previous command has to be executed.



